In the Matter of Orville E. HANSEN, Debtor, The FIRST NATIONAL BANK OF TEKAMAH, NEBRASKA, Appellee, v. Orville E. HANSEN and Virginia Hansen, Appellants. No. 83-1223. United States Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. March 23, 1983.

Before HEANEY, BRIGHT and ROSS, Circuit Judges.

ORDER

For the reasons stated in No. 83-1158, 702 F.2d 728 (8th Cir.1983), this cross-appeal is dismissed.

It is so ordered.
